  "title": "international students recruitment",
  "description": "<p>Sales Supervisor (International Market – Education Sector)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>BizChamp International College</p>\n<p>116 Middle Road, #04-02, ICB Enterprise House, Singapore 188972</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>About the Role / 职位简介</p>\n<p>We are seeking a driven, motivated, and responsible individual who is ready to grow a long-term career with us. As a Sales Supervisor, you will lead international recruitment efforts for pre-university and diploma programmes, focusing on building partnerships and expanding new markets. This is an exciting opportunity for someone who is passionate about education, confident in leadership, and eager to achieve success together with the team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>我们正在寻找一位有责任心、积极进取并渴望成长的人才，加入我们的团队并与我们共同发展事业。作为销售主管，您将负责国际市场的招生拓展及合作伙伴关系的建立，推广学院的大学预科及文凭课程。此职位非常适合有热情、有目标，并希望与团队共同成长的候选人。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities / 工作职责</p>\n<p>\t•\tDevelop and implement strategies to grow international student recruitment.</p>\n<p>\t•\tSupervise and guide the sales team to achieve enrolment goals.</p>\n<p>\t•\tBuild and maintain strong relationships with agents, schools, and education partners.</p>\n<p>\t•\tIdentify new market opportunities and manage promotional activities.</p>\n<p>\t•\tCoordinate with academic and admissions departments to ensure a smooth enrolment process.</p>\n<p>\t•\tPrepare regular reports and updates on sales performance.</p>\n<p>\t•\t制定并执行市场拓展及招生策略。</p>\n<p>\t•\t带领及指导销售团队达成招生目标。</p>\n<p>\t•\t维护与教育代理、学校及合作伙伴的良好关系。</p>\n<p>\t•\t发掘新市场机会并策划推广活动。</p>\n<p>\t•\t与学术及招生部门紧密配合，确保招生流程顺利。</p>\n<p>\t•\t定期汇报销售进展及市场反馈。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements / 任职要求</p>\n<p>\t•\tDiploma or Degree in Marketing, Business, or related discipline.</p>\n<p>\t•\tAt least 3 years of relevant experience in education sales or international marketing.</p>\n<p>\t•\tExcellent communication and interpersonal skills in English (ability to communicate in another language is an advantage for liaising with international partners).</p>\n<p>\t•\tStrong sense of responsibility, self-motivation, and teamwork spirit.</p>\n<p>\t•\tPassionate about education and willing to grow with the organisation.</p>\n<p>\t•\t拥有市场营销、商业管理或相关专业的文凭或学位。</p>\n<p>\t•\t至少三年教育销售或国际市场拓展经验。</p>\n<p>\t•\t具备良好的英语沟通能力，能使用其他语言者更佳（以便与国际伙伴沟通）。</p>\n<p>\t•\t有责任感、自我驱动力强、具备团队合作精神。</p>\n<p>\t•\t对教育事业充满热情，愿意与机构共同成长。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>What We Offer / 我们提供</p>\n<p>\t•\tSupportive and dynamic work environment with career advancement opportunities.</p>\n<p>\t•\tProfessional development and training support.</p>\n<p>\t•\tAttractive remuneration based on performance.</p>\n<p>\t•\t充满活力与支持性的工作环境，提供晋升机会。</p>\n<p>\t•\t专业培训及发展支持。</p>\n<p>\t•\t有吸引力的薪酬待遇及表现奖励机制。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Work Location / 工作地点</p>\n<p>116 Middle Road, #04-02, ICB Enterprise House, Singapore 188972</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Employment Type / 职位类型</p>\n<p>Full-Time / 全职</p>",
